jei.pokefood.mixing_info:
Pastries such as poké-puffs and poffins can be made in the mixers using 4 ingredients, the resulting item will change based on the flavors of said ingredients.

Poké-Puff need 2 berries and 2 other ingredients such as fruits, honey, tea and more. The amount of flavors will change the quality of the resulting poké-puff.
Poffin dough can be made using 2 berries, 1 milk bucket and 1 other ingredients like for a poké-puff.

"Replacement powders" can be used in place of berries, but those only have one flavor each.
